          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use the Advanced Repair Protocol without other Aliangé products?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, both products can be integrated into any existing skincare routine. However, their results are amplified when used within the Aliangé system — the Biocinamide Serum strengthens the barrier for optimal exosome absorption, the Jellyfish Peptide Serum provides complementary collagen stimulation via different peptide pathways, and the Daily Devotion Cleanser ensures the skin is properly prepared without barrier compromise. The Advanced Repair Protocol is most powerful when layered onto The Protocol or Essential Protocol as a targeted enhancement.</p>"
